Program: Discovery
Title: Fuelling the Future - gas and oil
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz39
Last Broadcast Date: 14 February 2006
A look at the fuels of the future. Richard Black gives an audit of the sources of energy we have exploited; from the deposits of coal and oil, which took millions of years to form, and the crops that take a year to grow, to the sources of uranium and other radioactive materials.